== Tips ==
You might want to disable the counting of folders in nautilus: Edit -> Preferences -> Preview and then set "Count number of items" to "Never"
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7706781/why-does-nautilus-read-directories-in-advance
gconftool-2 --type string --set /apps/nautilus/preferences/ show_directory_item_counts never

